            <title>[LU-7435] ost-pools defect: suite is not functional on config MGS/MDS not combined</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7435</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ost-pools is to be fixed to be run on configuration:&lt;br/&gt;
MGS/MDS not combined, different nodes, configured as failover pair&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Lustre Manual Chapter_19.2:&lt;br/&gt;
Another requirement for managing OST pools is to &quot;either have the MDT and MGS on the same node&quot; or have a Lustre client mounted on the MGS node, if it is separate from the MDS.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
